{
  "texts": [
    "The main character Elara wants to become a memory curator to operate the memory database.",
    "At the same time, she has a genuine interest in the ethics of memory modification and want to explore the Eclipsed Echoes more deeply.",
    "Together with her friend Liam, Elara explores the world of the Memory Echoes, uncovering secrets linked to her family's past and competing with her main enemy Dr Malloy.",
    "3 Romance \"Love on the line\" There are two parallel storylines in this concept: Emma and Max love story at the present day and Evelyn and James love story a few decades ago.",
    "Emma and Max meet each other by chance in a stalled subway car, discover that are quite different, but want to spend time together."
